<p>This famed Pozieres" Wood was a stumbling block in the way of our advance &amp; had to be taken somehow so thats how they decided to give us a chance to prove ourselves, to look at it, it is nothing more than a straggling line of trees all stripped of every leaf &amp; branch they might have once possessed by the torrent of shells that had been poured into it, there was an odd orchard scattered about it &amp; a small village or two in it, the German line ran round the edge of it, &amp; inside it was all trenches &amp; guns, a most formidable thing</p>
